{"ID":"20250708131530-si2w3ba","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20250708131530-si2w3ba","title":"待办","type":"doc","updated":"20260611103842"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260611103553-7965kh7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260611103553-7965kh7","updated":"20260611103553"}},{"ID":"20260611103553-uh1ppm9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260611103553-uh1ppm9","updated":"20260611103753"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"需请产品设计团队确保当前的外审计划按目标完成，针对830迭代，需项目、产品、交互设计梳理当前既定范围的详细外审计划"}]},{"ID":"20260611103452-rb1qc39","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260611103452-rb1qc39","updated":"20260611103452"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"快控中心-PPV阶段看是否先提前输出首页方案@chengyut"}]},{"ID":"20260611103452-nhsso67","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260611103452-nhsso67","updated":"20260611103452"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"明确一下方控安卓框架验证的具体工作内容，会议建议系统框架验证应前置于应用开发@钱 @进"}]},{"ID":"20260611103452-mo3694y","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260611103452-mo3694y","updated":"20260611103452"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"figma 管理员账号/权限，需结合支付方式等因素，与斑马专题确认方案@叶"}]},{"ID":"20260611103452-033oimw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260611103452-033oimw","updated":"20260611103452"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"FM1 EP阶段改制实车，看PM是否能继续支持一台"}]},{"ID":"20260611103452-ggmdcda","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260611103452-ggmdcda","updated":"20260611103452"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"外部控制器如IPD的联调需求，建议请外部基于接口不变，先行在8295平台启动验证，@许水华"}]},{"ID":"20260611103452-vc5rbek","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260611103452-vc5rbek","updated":"20260611103501"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"评估下当前公版Q音SDK 适配cover flow是否有额外开发费用及工作量@薛@xiaorui"}]},{"ID":"20260611103452-8z5i17a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260611103452-8z5i17a","updated":"20260611103842"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"爱奇艺H5评估基于VGUI优化是否能达到AGUI的相当效果，给个排期；针对安卓环境的H5方案，产品牵头专题拉BM‘爱